  "title": "No More Rain!",
  "description": "Removes rain weather particles!",
  "body": "**What is this do?**\n- This resourcepack is made to remove the rain particles from your screen completely, to reduce eyestrain!\n\n**Why does it Exist?**\n- It's part of a series of small projects I'm working on to remove flashing or rapidly moving textures from the game that may cause issues for people with Migraines, Photosensitivity, or Epilepsy.\n\n**Are you going to keep this updated?**\n- Yes! I plan on releasing updates for this for as long as I continue to play the game <3",
